825
01:37:00.590 --> 01:37:05.299
- Macking... Hanging.
- I like that.

826
01:37:05.511 --> 01:37:10.885
Macking... Hanging.
Macking... Hanging.

827
01:37:16.272 --> 01:37:21.693
- Ain't that Nichole?
