842
01:38:48.029 --> 01:38:50.485
But you're dancing with me.

843
01:39:07.757 --> 01:39:10.045
So. how cold is it back east?

844
01:39:59.308 --> 01:40:01.680
Let's start this off.

845
01:40:05.564 --> 01:40:13.393
You got the good sound.
This is the best man's toast. Get up.

846
01:40:13.613 --> 01:40:17.065
