852
01:40:53.569 --> 01:40:56.274
I did a lot of thinking.

853
01:40:58.491 --> 01:41:01.776
And I came to a funny conclusion.

854
01:41:02.870 --> 01:41:05.195
I realised how selfish I was.

855
01:41:06.040 --> 01:41:11.331
Because I felt like
I was losing a very dear friend.

856
01:41:11.545 --> 01:41:16.373
That may not sound
like the right thing to say.

857
01:41:16.592 --> 01:41:21.337
But I moved around a lot as a boy
and never knew what it was like -

858
01:41:21.555 --> 01:41:29.681
