until I met Roland and Levinio.

859
01:41:29.897 --> 01:41:32.649
You need to stop.

860
01:41:32.858 --> 01:41:39.525
So today I'm a bit upset.
but I'm also very happy -

861
01:41:39.740 --> 01:41:44.069
