866
01:42:01.178 --> 01:42:06.136
To our parents. you know we love
you all and thanks for all the love.

867
01:42:07.976 --> 01:42:13.101
And to the two grown men
who mean the most to me. -

868
01:42:14.816 --> 01:42:18.896
